  </div>

  <!-- ─── Funded Stage Drawdowns ─────────────────────────────────── -->
  <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Funded Stage Drawdowns</h3>
  <p class="mb-4">
    Funded-stage risk limits differ by programme. These drawdowns are measured from the initial funded balance.
  </p>
  <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-slate-200 mb-8">
    <table class="w-full text-sm">
      <thead class="bg-slate-50 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide">
        <tr>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Funded Rule</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-center">1-Step Funded</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-center">2-Step Funded</th>
